### Detection Priority

```rust
pub fn should_use_rich_output() -> bool {
    // Priority order (first match wins):
    // 1. DCG_NO_RICH=1 → false
    if std::env::var("DCG_NO_RICH").is_ok() {
        return false;
    }

    // 2. CI=true → false
